        <abstract>
            <para>The simplified classification of Maricopa Association of Governments (MAG) land
                use map is created by combining the original land use categories into 5 major
                classes - urban, agriculture, recreation, desert, and other. This has been done for
                land use/land cover monitoring purposes and to compare the 2000 land use map with
                historic land use layers including the 1995 MAG land use map.</para>
